node.accessibility_caption: A collage of five in-game photos, arranged two on the left, three on the right. From left, top to bottom, then right; photo by @wintermut_e of Eivor in a white cloak on a pale horse; photo by @TheLordMarvel of Havi in closeup, face shrouded by a hood; photo by @G_Assassin90 of a river rounding a bend; photo by @Malley0818 of Alexios, silhouetted by a sunset; photo by @ChrisVP88 of flora among an expanse of dunes.

An in-game photo of Assassin’s Creed Valhalla by wintermut_e on Twitter. The photo shows Eivor, wearing a white cloak emblazoned with a red cross and its hood raised, riding a pale horse flecked with black spots. They stand knee-deep in a field filled with vibrant crimson flowers, with several white flowers in their proximity. A blue-tinged fog covers the middle and far-distance of a forest and overcast sky.

An in-game photo of Assassin’s Creed Valhalla by TheLordMarvel on Twitter. The photo shows an extreme closeup of Havi, with his entire face besides the tip of his nose and beneath completely shrouded by a dark hood. A linear tattoo etches down Havi’s lip before disappearing into a brown beard. The visage hidden by the grey garment is surrounded in like darkness.

An in-game photo of Assassin’s Creed Valhalla by G_Assassin90 on Twitter. The photo shows a curving, shallow riverbed that rounds a bend filled with tall greenery. Several waterfowl float lazily on the water. Beyond is a regal, multi-story building with a second story and rooftop that peeks over the treetops. The sky is a rich blue with several massive clouds.

An in-game photo of Assassin’s Creed Odyssey by Malley0818 on Twitter. The photo shows Alexios, silhouetted by the setting sun with blades in hand as he completes an attack. One arm is extended behind him, sword pointed away from his body, the other rounds his mid-section. He stands atop a thin layer of water that reflects the rich amber light of the sunset and the shadows of distant clouds.

An in-game photo of Assassin’s Creed Origins by ChrisVP88 on Twitter. The photo shows a small gathering of bushes and trees among an expanse of dunes with the sun beating down on the sand. One tree leans harshly to the side, while the other has a collection of brush at its base. A mountain range looms in the background, shrouded by distance and clouds on the horizon.
Photo by Assassin's Creed on August 19, 2021.
